            SET name = ?, description = ?, model_configuration_id = ?, creativity_level = ?, temperature = ?, top_p = ?,

                max_context_words = ?, max_generation_words = ?, supports_streaming = ?, supports_unfiltered = ?, is_active = ?
            WHERE id = ?
